H0.text: What is the name of the official British coronation crown. Imperial State Crown

H1.text: What is the name of the official British coronation crown. Sovereign's Sceptre Crown

H2.text: What is the name of the official British coronation crown. Crown of Charlemagne

H3.text: What is the name of the official British coronation crown. St Edwards crown

A4.text: St Edward's Crown is the coronation crown of the Crown Jewels of the United Kingdom.

A5.text: It was placed on the high altar and formally used again at the 2023 coronation of Charles III, marking its return as the principal coronation crown of the sovereign.
